{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li0 \fi0 5 Real-World Example Workflow\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li0 \fi0 You say:  "List all files in D:\\RAJAREDDY_FILE_MCP"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li0 \fi0 Claude calls: filesystem:list_directory(\{ path: "D:\\RAJAREDDY_FILE_MCP" \})\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li0 \fi0 Plugin \u8594?  [\{ name: "How_File_MCP_Plugin_Works.html", size: 12400, ... \}]\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li0 \fi0 Claude says: "Found 1 file: How_File_MCP_Plugin_Works.html (12 KB)"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li0 \fi0 6 Security & Safety\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li0 \fi0 \u55357?\u56594?\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel3 \b \fs24 Sandboxed Access\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The plugin only accesses paths and drives that have been explicitly configured and permitted.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li0 \fi0 \u9989?\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel3 \b \fs24 Explicit Confirmation\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Destructive operations like delete or overwrite are always confirmed before execution.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li0 \fi0 \u55357?\u56523?\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel3 \b \fs24 Audit Trail\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Every file operation is logged so you can track what was created, modified, or deleted.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li0 \fi0 \u55357?\u57003?\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel3 \b \fs24 No Remote Transfer\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The plugin operates entirely on your local machine \u8212- no data is sent to external servers.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li0 \fi0 \u55357?\u57057?\u65039?\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel3 \b \fs24 Permission Checks\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Respects OS-level file permissions and will not bypass system security restrictions.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li0 \fi0 \u55357?\u56592?\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel3 \b \fs24 Structured Protocol\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 All tool calls follow a strict schema, preventing arbitrary or malformed operations.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li0 \fi0 7 Key Benefits\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Speed:} Accomplish complex file tasks in seconds using plain English.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Intelligence:} Claude can organize, rename, and structure files smartly based on context.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Automation:} Chain multiple file operations together in a single conversation.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Multi-Drive Support:} Works across all available drives \u8212- C:, D:, and network drives.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Cross-Platform:} Compatible with Windows, macOS, and Linux file systems.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Natural Language:} No commands to memorize \u8212- just describe what you want done.\sa180\par}
